<div class="badge warning-badge">Password Reset</div>

<h1 class="title">Reset Your Password</h1>
<p class="subtitle">You requested a password reset for your DeployIO account. Click the button below to create a new password.</p>

<div class="highlight-box">
  {{#if resetLink}}
  {{> button url=resetLink label="Reset Your Password"}}
  {{/if}}
  <p style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; color: #737373; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; text-align: center;">
    This secure link expires in {{expiresIn}}
  </p>
</div>

<div class="security-info">
  <strong>Security Information:</strong>
  <ul style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #a8a29e;">
    <li>This password reset link can only be used once</li>
    <li>If you didn't request this reset, you can safely ignore this email</li>
    <li>Your current password remains active until you create a new one</li>
    <li>For security, this link will expire automatically</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<p style="color: #737373; margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px;">
  For security reasons, if you need another reset link, please request a new one from the 
  <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="text-link">login page</a>.
</p>